\v 3 P…ôh kot…ôni-vivi Uhg…®n, u in Uhg…®n m…®ne Tat…ô r…ôha I…ôrm…ôn…®g r…ôhatah Iesu Kr…®sto. In Tat…ô i…ôt…ôm in n…ôuk…ôt…® nas…ôk…ôhruini…ôn, k…ôni in Uhg…®n i…ôt…ôm nasirui…ôn r…ôfin o n…ôf…ôri…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn tats…®p…ôn ohni.\x - \xo 1:3  \xt Rom 15:5\x*  
\v 4 In t…ôt…ôf…ôri n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôhatah e n…ôrahi…ôn r…ôfin r…ôhatah m…ôm…ô kitah kot…ôhrun n…ôf…ôri…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ômimi e n…ôrahi…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n. K…ôni kitah kot…ôf…ôri n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôhalah e noli…ôn r…ôha n…ôf…ôri…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol k…ôm tah.  
\v 5 T…ôhmen …ôm…ô e nahm…ôi…ôn i…ôt…ôm Kr…®sto t…ômos, t…ômuva m…®n e n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhatah. K…ôni e noli…ôn …ôhmen …ôm…ô, Kr…®sto in suaru m…ôm…ô nasirui…ôn o n…ôf…ôri…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôhatah t…ômuva p…®k e n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhatah, k…ôni r…ôueiu nasirui…ôn r…ôhatah o n…ôf…ôri…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn tatuv…ôn m…®n o n…ôt…ômimi p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.\x - \xo 1:5  \xt Sam 34:19\x*   
