\v 5 It…ômah aru, otakil vivi n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah. ?N…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah in p…ôhri…ôn, u…ô k…ôp…ô? It…ômah aru, n…ôkoteruh vivi r…ôhat…ômah noli…ôn. ?N…ôkot…ôhrun u…ô k…ôp…ô, m…ôm…ô Kr…®sto Iesu t…ôtat…®g e n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah? !M…ôt…ôu n…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômah n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn t…ôs…®t…ôu-p…ôni…ôn noli…ôn r…ôha n…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn, k…ôni Kr…®sto t…ôsat…®gi…ôn e n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhat…ômah!\x - \xo 13:5  \xt 1Kor 11:28\x*  
