\s1 Naunun n…ôghati…ôn  
\p
\v 11 Piak m…®n m…®ne n…ôuv…®n…®k m…®n. Inu r…ôhak naunun n…ôghati…ôn. Otagi…ôn. Ot…ôuhlin r…ôhat…ômah noli…ôn m…®n. Ot…ôt…ôu r…ôhak n…ôghati…ôn. Τèhuva e n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn k…ôti…ôh. Otat…®g e n…ôm…ôlinui…ôn. K…ôni Uhg…®n r…ôha nolkeikei…ôn m…®ne n…ôm…ôlinui…ôn otat…®g it…ômah min.   
